{"tid":198283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洋人電音趴踢「被蛇咬」　台女雙膝下跪助「排毒」","createTime":"2017-04-12T11:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T16:25:04.000Z","uid":35964,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b0df4dde69d37aa934629e98b0adebb758d2c87","tid":198283,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"什麼是台灣最美的風景？臉書粉絲頁「靠北電子音樂」，昨天凌晨有人投稿一張照片，表示有一名外國男子在台灣參加電子音樂節，但不小心「被蛇咬傷了」。還好有一名台灣女子二話不說幫他急救、「吸毒」，當場救了男生一命。照片一出，網友紛紛表示意見。「發揮大愛、乃中華民國最佳精神」「台灣女生捨身救人 超讚的」「這位女施主捨己救人的行為 ，太令人敬佩了」（法庭中心／綜合報導） <br />\n<br />\n以下是臉書原文 <br />\n有一名外國男子在台灣參加最大的電子音樂節 <br />\n不慎遭蛇咬傷 <br />\n一名台灣女子二話不說幫他急救吸毒 <br />\n救了他一命 <br />\n台灣最美的風景。人 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/u9XrGLsl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fu9XrGLsl.jpg&h=4e16bd46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3602e36bfac5a1f435839923052e471d5e0c129d","tid":198283,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"我相信香港女仔都有依種大愛精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbfea8c9d3fd15a5b96e3f70e9005d05ee37169","tid":198283,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319b286a434e806ff21ef60e0713d34f8cb4edb0","tid":198283,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"港女最愛"},{"pid":"0e62564bc680965d411a08585511cfba900bda26","tid":198283,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"拿，呢d就真係積口德啦"},{"pid":"3cd1d20c04fa70e8e784a09c75a48a80213ebbf4","tid":198283,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:59:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"821ed09c89ef5ec3567e7043bb72b7dbb1154833","tid":198283,"uid":35882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11: